node.text: I am blown away by the love and support from my RIVERDALE family, the best cast and crew on the planet. This video means everything to me, my mom, my brother, and my sister. Getting the word out about what’s been happening in Nicaragua to my dad and so many others fighting for freedom and democracy is vital and may be life-saving. Follow the link in my bio to raise your voice in opposition to the outrageous violation of human rights being perpetrated against many innocent Nicaraguans. My heart goes out to all the families who have had their loved ones incarcerated unjustly by the Ortega regime. ❤️☮️🇺🇸🔙🇳🇮💪🏼

node.text: Throwback Thursday. A year ago today, I was working on a pilot about the Brides of Dracula with my fave partner-in-crime @maggiekiley.director. Starring the Queen of All Things @iamginatorres as Cleopatra. And @goran_visnjic as the suavest of Counts. And @erinrrichards as the saucy Madame de Sade. And @k8r3is as sweet, innocent Lily. Like so many other projects, we were shut down by the virus. A year later, the ladies haven’t seen the light of day…yet. But here’s a taste of the delicious, vampy fun we were working on…🔥👰🏽👰🏻👰🏼🧛🏻‍♂️🩸🖤💰🎭⭐️👀💥 📺

node.text: We truly saved the best...and scariest...for last. So much love for this cast, crew, writers, and fandom. Part Four finds our witches and mortals facing off against the Eldritch Terrors. And, friends, there will be monsters, sacrifices, last kisses, a satanic battle-of-the-bands, and some very, very special guest stars...before the most epic ending EVER. You are cordially invited to the End of All Things on December 31st, 2020. 🔮🖤🎢🌪⌛️🔥

node.text: If you haven’t watched #KatyKeene, #Riverdale’s sister-show, all episodes are available for streaming on #HBO Max starting midnight tonight!! There is so much HEART in this show--and lots of hearts, too! It’s a romantic-musical-comedy-drama-fairytale-dream set and filmed in the real NYC!! Love these actors, led by @lucyhale and @iamamurray, love this crew, and love these writers and editors. Settle into a warm bubble bath--or blow a few bubbles with your hand soap--and start binging!!! ❤️💋💃🏻👠🧨🍒👗📺👨🏻‍💻🏆

node.text: This week’s #Riverdale is a BIG Veronica Lodge episode. @camimendes ALWAYS brings it in EVERY scene, but she is SHOW-STOPPING in one with Hiram at her mercy. It’s a beautiful piece of acting. Truly a spellbinding dance of death. Also…Chad gets what’s coming to him at long last. Down to our final three… ♟🎰🥊🥂🔥🌪🚀⌛️💸💣🔪⚰️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Roberto Aguirre-Sacasa on September 19, 2021 tagging @arturoluissoria, and @rattlestickny. May be a closeup of 1 person and text that says 'NI MI MADRE WRITTEN PERFORME AND ARTURO LUÍS SORIA'.

node.text: Another soul-filling night at the theater this weekend. If you’re in New York, do whatever you can to see @arturoluissoria’s “Ni Mi Madre” at the @rattlestickny. A son’s love-letter to his mother. Their relationship rendered in all its complexity. In English and Spanish and Portuguese. So brutally honest and funny and moving. Like “Pass Over,” it’s not just a play, it’s a conjuring. A magic spell. EXTENDED THROUGH THE 25TH!! P.S. It’s only an hour long, but I didn’t want it to end. And when I walked out of the theater, it felt like I’d been on a beach in Brazil. ⭐️💥💃🏽🎭🎟

node.text: On the eve of our dad’s 50th day in prison, my sister and I spent the day in DC meeting with members of Congress and senior level staffers. @maelvirasalazar, @repgregorymeeks Patrick Ventrell @statedept. It is imperative that the House pass the RENACER ACT to hold the Ortega regime accountable for their actions. I implore @speakerpelosi to bring it to the House floor for a vote IMMEDIATELY. #freefrancisco #sosnicaragua 🙏🏼🇺🇸🔙🇳🇮💪🏼☮️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Roberto Aguirre-Sacasa on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Today marks the bicentennial of Central America’s Independence Day. In Nicaragua, it should be a day of celebration. It’s not. Instead, the freedom that so many Nicaraguans have fought for over the years doesn’t exist. President Ortega and his wife, Vice President Murillo, have turned a democracy into a ruthless dictatorship that traffics in terror and oppression. They have dismantled the free press and shut down all the voices that would have challenged them in the upcoming elections. In recent months, they’ve jailed more than 30 opposition leaders, students, reporters, business leaders, human rights activists, and members of civil society, including my father. Most recently, they’ve ordered the arrest of exiled Nicaraguan writer Sergio Ramirez. Another exile living in Costa Rica, the protestor Joao Maldonado, was gunned down over the weekend. He clings to life. Today, on Nicaragua’s Independence Day, we pray for him and for all the Nicaraguans who are fighting to preserve democratic freedom in their country. #freefrancisco #sosnicaragua 🙏🏼 🇺🇸 🔙🇳🇮 ☮️

Everything starts weaving together in this, the first of our FINAL FOUR!! (Another fun fact about tonight’s episode: It’s our second in a row directed by Queen Supreme @robingivens —thank you, Robin!!!!) Tune in and watch live!!! 💪🏼🔥💃🏽👽👀🫀🏃🏻‍♂️👠👑🐀🌪💥☠️

node.text: There’s an all-new #Riverdale on Wednesday. But the big event of the week is @lilireinhart birthday today!!! I think back to the day Lili tested for the pilot. She came in and performed her two scenes—one with Archie in the diner, one with Alice in her bedroom—and after she left the room, the head of WBTV turned to everyone and said, simply: “Well, that’s our Betty.” Truer words have NEVER been spoken in that audition room in Building 140. Who could have guessed that fateful afternoon that we’d still be on a journey together now some five (!!) years later. Eternally in awe of her talent. Eternally grateful for her heart. Love you dearly, Lili. Our Betty 4EVER. ❤️⭐️🌹🎂🎉

node.text: I am blown away by the love and support from my RIVERDALE family, the best cast and crew on the planet. This video means everything to me, my mom, my brother, and my sister. Getting the word out about what’s been happening in Nicaragua to my dad and so many others fighting for freedom and democracy is vital and may be life-saving. Follow the link in my bio to raise your voice in opposition to the outrageous violation of human rights being perpetrated against many innocent Nicaraguans. My heart goes out to all the families who have had their loved ones incarcerated unjustly by the Ortega regime. ❤️☮️🇺🇸🔙🇳🇮💪🏼

node.text: Tomorrow night, we meet a VERY different Josie McCoy in this week’s #Riverdale (aka The Return of the Pussycats) and @iamamurray is simply SPELLBINDING in the episode. Her journey started in Riverdale; it continued in New York, in #KatyKeene; this week…the super-star comes home. And there will be ALL KINDS of reunions and reckonings. Unmissable. 💃🏽⭐️🎤🎼💋
